title: Lootfest Ready-made Underfoot Client for EQEmulator - lootfest.g
description:
This is a custom refined UF (Underfoot) level client for the Everquest Emulator (eqemulator.net) server called LOOTFEST ... The files have been custom updated as of April 20th, 2014 , and more information on the server can be found at http://Lootfest.Guildlaunch.com ... there is a vanilla compile of macroquest2 (macroquest2.com) from the good folks at MQEmulator.net 

This client is not intended for use with any other server, but with the right knowledge, can probably be used with several other custom source code servers on eqemulator.net , provided all custom files are replaced with the target servers files. If Lootfest's custom files have changed at the time you are downloading this torrent, simply go to lootfest website and replace all those recently updated custom files. Thank you and have a nice day! Come play with us on LOOTFEST!
